  "notes": "## Zahlungsabgleich v3 (Payment Auto-Matching with GoCardless Open Banking)\n\n### Changes in v3\n- Added proper token refresh (POST /token/new/) instead of static env var token\n- Changed from 7-day to 2-day lookback window (daily sync, less overlap)\n- Added transaction dedup check against gocardless_transactions table\n- Added INSERT to gocardless_transactions for full audit trail\n- Implemented 3-tier matching with confidence scores:\n  - Tier 1 (95%): Invoice number (nummer) found in Verwendungszweck\n  - Tier 2 (85%): Exact amount + partial customer name match\n  - Tier 3 (70%): Amount within +/-1% tolerance\n- Added INSERT buchungen for bookkeeping integration\n- Added UPDATE gocardless_transactions with match result\n- Added Telegram notification for matched payments\n- Unmatched credits logged for manual review with gc_transaction_db_id reference\n\n### Env Vars Required\n1. **GOCARDLESS_SECRET_ID** - GoCardless API secret ID\n2. **GOCARDLESS_SECRET_KEY** - GoCardless API secret key\n3. **GOCARDLESS_ACCOUNT_ID** - Bank account UUID from GoCardless\n4. **TENANT_ID** - Supabase tenant UUID\n5. **TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN** - (optional) Telegram bot token for notifications\n6. **TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID** - (optional) Telegram chat ID for notifications\n\n### Setup\n1. Register at https://bankaccountdata.gocardless.com (free, 100 req/day)\n2. Create a requisition for the business bank account\n3. Set env vars in n8n\n4. Run migration-gocardless-banking.sql in Supabase\n5. Activate this workflow\n\n### Scheduling\n- Daily at 07:00 Berlin time (1 hour before dunning check at 08:00)\n- 2-day lookback catches delayed bookings while minimizing API calls\n\n### API Limits\n- GoCardless free tier: 100 API requests/day\n- This workflow uses ~4 requests per run (token + transactions + dedup queries)\n- Well within free tier limits"
}
